-- De Beers Says its Considering Offers for Two South African Diamond Mines
-- Antony Sguazzin
-- 2010-07-29T14:51:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/de-beers-says-its-considering-offers-for-two-south-african-diamond-mines.html

          
          
             De Beers has received offers for its
Namaqualand and Finsch mines in South Africa, which will be
evaluated, it said in an e-mailed statement today.  
          
          


  


        